# Quick Start
## Live E320 Mode
### Step 1) Run the launcher
```bash
./launch_e320_spectrogram.sh \
  --freq 102700000 \
  --rate 1000000 \
  --gain 40 \
  --ant RX2 \
  --no-sigmf

Step 2) View the GUI

The spectrum and waterfall window should open automatically.

Step 3) Stop

Close the GUI window or press Ctrl+C.

⸻

Synthetic Test Mode

Step 1) Create the FIFO

rm -f /tmp/e320_iq.pipe
mkfifo /tmp/e320_iq.pipe

Step 2) Start the synthetic generator

python3 synthetic_blocker.py > /tmp/e320_iq.pipe

Step 3) Launch the GUI

python3 waterfall_sigmf.py \
  --fifo /tmp/e320_iq.pipe \
  --samp-rate 1000000 \
  --center-freq 102700000 \
  --no-sigmf

Step 4) Stop

Press Ctrl+C in the synthetic generator terminal and close the GUI.
